These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: bridge, chess
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, country
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
2. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person playing bridge##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Game      | bridge  | chess   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Music-Genre         | country | house |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, chestnut
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the malaysian is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Nationality          | canadian     | malaysian |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Color     | lilac   | chestnut    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, nectarine
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
House: victorian, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Food         | nectarine | broccoli    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| House   | victorian         | farmhouse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
