2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Flower         | iris | marigold     |
| Color   | green  | chestnut         |

