.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, swisher
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the swisher-smoker is the dutch##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Cigar           | swisher | dannemann    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Movie-Genre         | musical    | zombie   |

