.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, february
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
House: colonial, ranch-style
1. the doctor is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
3. the colonial house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Birthday    | april | february    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| House   | colonial        | ranch-style     |

 